Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.70,0:22:53.87,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Waiting for your touch
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.29,0:22:59.38,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}No,don't give up on life
