Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.22,0:23:15.02,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}こぼれてく記憶の砂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.10,0:23:18.90,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}芽生えた想いまで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.98,0:23:23.86,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}ねえ　こんなに呆気なく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.82,0:23:31.16,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}消えてしまうの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.16,0:23:32.41,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I wish I was there
