Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.93,0:23:50.05,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}No,don't give up on life
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.26,0:23:52.14,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}This endless dead end
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.35,0:23:56.60,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}君を砕くこの悲しみが
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.02,0:24:02.15,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}いつか終わりますように
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.19,0:24:05.78,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}For now I'll see you off
